  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Your Precision and Patience!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform breathtaking Trickshots that you’ve only seen in videos - all with your own hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Precision: Use mouse controls to throw various objects and hit tiny targets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extremely Challenging: Even the smallest adjustment can completely change the outcome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time-Consuming Masterpieces: Some Trickshots may take tens of minutes or even hours to accomplish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultimate Reward: Push through the difficulty, feel your skills improve, and enjoy an unmatched sense of accomplishment.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share Your Epic Trickshots</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every successful Trickshot is recorded as a replay video. Share your accomplishments with friends or the world on social media.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay videos (MP4) are not supported by Steam Cloud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Balancing a card between two objects.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.poster.avif?t=1738788195\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.webm?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.mp4?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rolling a marble to stop perfectly in the dot of a dice.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/075d116d85458f613216d6d1a898457b.poster.avif?t=1738788195\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/075d116d85458f613216d6d1a898457b.webm?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/075d116d85458f613216d6d1a898457b.mp4?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nailing a bottle flip on top of a tiny dice.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/5533b00da3c5b29111f77cea963eab0c.poster.avif?t=1738788195\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/5533b00da3c5b29111f77cea963eab0c.webm?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/5533b00da3c5b29111f77cea963eab0c.mp4?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take on the challenge and make these incredible Trickshots your own!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming Policy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to stream and upload videos of TrickShot Simulator gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no restrictions on monetization, whether you are an individual or a corporation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the game and share it with the world!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Your Precision and Patience!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform breathtaking Trickshots that you’ve only seen in videos - all with your own hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Precision: Use mouse controls to throw various objects and hit tiny targets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extremely Challenging: Even the smallest adjustment can completely change the outcome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time-Consuming Masterpieces: Some Trickshots may take tens of minutes or even hours to accomplish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultimate Reward: Push through the difficulty, feel your skills improve, and enjoy an unmatched sense of accomplishment.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share Your Epic Trickshots</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every successful Trickshot is recorded as a replay video. Share your accomplishments with friends or the world on social media.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay videos (MP4) are not supported by Steam Cloud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Balancing a card between two objects.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.poster.avif?t=1738788195\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.webm?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384190/extras/c11dd8a99eed18041ece86e89cc3b0ad.mp4?t=1738788195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rolling a marble to stop perfectly in the dot of a dice.</h2><p